1. Which feature allows an admin to set filters based on user fields so that specific actions are visible only to certain users?
Ans : A. Dynamic actions

2. Which type of view is now available for leads, contacts, and accounts?
Ans : D. Intelligence

3. After turning on the Lead Intelligence View, what additional step must an admin take for users to see it?
Ans : B. Add the Intelligence View button to the Lead List View in Setup.

4. How does a user return to the original list view from the Contact Intelligence View?
Ans : B. Click List View in the button menu.

5. In the Account Intelligence View, how does a user view insights on an account?
Ans : B. Click the icon beside a record name to open the side panel and view all available insights.
